{"tid":831112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT人入]點解Image Coor 係Y axis向下 點解Spherical Coor 係零度向右","createTime":"2018-09-21T16:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:23:47.000Z","uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96d899be675f70e954542bee0500d1dfce544fb3","tid":831112,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"細個學X向左 Y向上 零度係向上 = 北<br />\n點解program上用咁大整蠱 call atan2(y, x)除左要記住零度向右 仲要記住佢y,x調轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得有佢嘅原因嘅 但諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他仲有唔少例子...諗到再講 e.g. geojson係 long, lat debug時喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11625ee267d4e31082211c8ce1843056dc823b0","tid":831112,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:14:00.000Z","msg":"細個學X向右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打出黎時自己都調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861614cf5c1c3bc29ccbc9ce7f9850e9cc2a9b65","tid":831112,"uid":51746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"因為program design唔係x y軸<br />\n<br />\n係用(row, column)"},{"pid":"28cd314d87dd6b38bb41f7e52f0a4fb10bb05335","tid":831112,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"861614cf5c1c3bc29ccbc9ce7f9850e9cc2a9b65","tid":831112,"uid":51746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"因為program design唔係x y軸<br />\n<br />\n係用(row, column)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁樣make sense好多 仲有無其他例子"},{"pid":"02d19045bb3fbb96b4613769f8cdfa4fab886e09","tid":831112,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"861614cf5c1c3bc29ccbc9ce7f9850e9cc2a9b65","tid":831112,"uid":51746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"因為program design唔係x y軸<br />\n<br />\n係用(row, column)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"但係又咁講 image上都無column/row names 所有都係pixel黎 咁樣學row column放有咩好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce503ea8272dee9a971f9aa1a87207e2c2a21ac","tid":831112,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為program design唔係x y軸<br />\n<br />\n係用(row, column)</blockquote>但係又咁講 image上都無column/row names 所有都係pixel黎 咁樣學row column放有咩好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrow column design係用黎做reference<br />\n<br />\n當你想搵(35421, 21580) 下10格右5格嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n你可以call (35421-10, 21580+5)"},{"pid":"6e7bf50c9146a4de96f6df2a0540edcb2d91afc7","tid":831112,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"因為以前crt moon係逐行掃描 <br />\n即係上至下，左至右<br />\n假設要畫一個3 * 3square<br />\n最簡單嘅方法<br />\n根住條rules<br />\n第一粒pixel 0,0 相對嚟講就係左上角<br />\npointer 向右(x axis +1) 填3 粒pixel<br />\npointer 向下(y axis +1) 重覆上面<br />\n如此類推<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"4c40c95a489aad551af550bb2635ce988cdbeb16","tid":831112,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T19:39:15.000Z","msg":"Maths習慣係由x軸開始逆時針計角<br />\n<br />\nY,x係因為y係分子"},{"pid":"f